  "code": "%% Phase 7 Startup Sequence\n%% Placeholder - to be expanded in Phase 7B\n\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant App as Application\n    participant Int as Integration\n    participant Stamp as stamp.json\n    participant Bundle as BUNDLE_ROOT\n\n    App->>Int: brok_app_open()\n    Int->>Stamp: Read stamp\n    alt Stamp missing or invalid\n        Int-->>App: Error: stamp invalid\n    else Stamp valid\n        Int->>Bundle: Check realpath match\n        Int->>Bundle: Check identity match\n        alt Match failed\n            Int-->>App: Error: mismatch\n        else Match succeeded\n            Int-->>App: Success: ready\n        end\n    end\n",
