  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个启动流程的时序图，描述应用打开时怎么验证 bundle 的完整性。核心逻辑是：App 调用 Integration 层，Integration 去读 stamp.json，然后和 BUNDLE_ROOT 做校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App",
        "Int",
        "Stamp",
        "Bundle",
        "brok_app_open"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，四个参与者：Application、Integration、stamp.json 和 BUNDLE_ROOT。第一步是 App 发起 brok_app_open() 调用到 Integration 对吧？然后 Integration 去读 stamp 文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App",
        "Int",
        "brok_app_open",
        "Stamp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。这里有个分支：如果 stamp.json 缺失或者格式不对，Integration 要直接返回错误给 App。只有 stamp 有效才继续往下走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Int",
        "Stamp",
        "App",
        "alt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主干画出来：App 到 Int 的 brok_app_open，然后 Int 到 Stamp 的读取操作。接着加个 alt 分支处理 stamp missing or invalid 的情况，错误返回给 App。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App-Int",
        "Int-Stamp",
        "alt",
        "Int--App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "stamp 有效的情况下，Integration 要去 BUNDLE_ROOT 做两道检查：realpath 匹配和 identity 匹配。这两步都过了才算成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Int",
        "Bundle",
        "realpath match",
        "identity match"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两道检查是顺序执行还是并行？还有，如果其中任何一道失败，是不是都要返回 mismatch 错误？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Int-Bundle",
        "Check realpath match",
        "Check identity match"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "顺序执行，先 realpath 再 identity。两个都成功才返回 ready，任一失败就报 mismatch。所以这里要嵌套一个 alt。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alt",
        "Match failed",
        "Match succeeded",
        "Int--App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。外层 alt 处理 stamp 是否有效，内层 alt 处理 bundle 校验结果。所有错误分支都返回给 App，成功分支返回 ready。",
